{"tid":20501,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"調查發現 99% 山寨 IPhone 充電器未能通過安全測試","createTime":"2016-12-03T11:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T14:32:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"803af62a7e3db7480abef951b31c69cfe4a8abc4","tid":20501,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:32:52.000Z","msg":"uk-3-pin-type-usb-charger-usb-cable-apple-iphone-5-5s-6-6s-plus-gradeone-1511-18-gradeone3<br />\n<br />\n雖然買電話會送充電器，不過相信不少人都有使用非原廠的充電器。最近一個調查則發現，99% 的山寨 iPhone 充電器並不合格，有可能帶來潛在危險。<br />\n<br />\n今次調查由英國貿易標準局 CTSI 委託進行，在全球 8 個國家網上購買了 400 個山寨充電器，然後測試其安全性能。結果在最基本的電流測試之中，只有 3 個可以成功防護電流衝擊，也就是說 99% 的山寨充電器連最基本的電流防護也欠奉，除了有機會損毀充電，更有可能傷害使用者。CTSI 的總裁表示，建議只在信任的供應商購買充電器，正版充電器雖然更貴，但山寨商品可能會損害你的家居，甚至自己或所愛的人的生命。<br />\n<br />\n之前 Apple 曾見調查過發現 Amazon 上面發售的 90% iPhone「原裝」充電器都是山寨貨，Amazon 也承認並表示會致力打擊此類商品。其實就算不買原裝充電器，也有不少品牌推出價錢合理的充電器，品質仍然比山寨貨要好，作為精明消費者要好好選擇。另外，如果充電器出現外殼裂開或者電線損壞的情況，就要立即停止使用，避免出現意外。<br />\n<br />\n來源：9to5Mac<br />\n<br />\n&bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=1b3955e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁 <a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=8d3740fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a>"},{"pid":"6ae6712e3df6d047c55bd6ea496c62ac669f00c4","tid":20501,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"咁都係新聞？"},{"pid":"9b01d02d01bc61c0ea423ff18539f0ba0f156aae","tid":20501,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9752122fc188862fe697f7cc17e073985252228","tid":20501,"uid":194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"有mfi既線係咪已經可以放心用？"},{"pid":"1d852bd1e3e355d12d9abcf89691c4aa21769eba","tid":20501,"uid":10439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T13:52:43.000Z","msg":"要買更係買xpower la"},{"pid":"e1746fc7036cfa29462ad28b0cddcb7bd6e1857b","tid":20501,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"你都識講係山寨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b93b68c25802ee8fcd064007e9fb4f8e0ebc0e4","tid":20501,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:31:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有mfi既線係咪已經可以放心用？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b97701b6180a5922448762ca830f57fd840e9b1","tid":20501,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要買更係買xpower la</blockquote><br />\n識買梗係唔買xpower<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}